00:00:14,488 --> 00:00:16,588
His name is Detective Conan!

8
00:01:56,826 --> 00:02:00,426
"Tohto Kokugikan"

9
00:02:00,726 --> 00:02:04,025
Now, let's have renown Detective Kogoro Mouri

