34
00:03:52,626 --> 00:03:54,225
All right!

35
00:03:54,226 --> 00:03:57,026
You're totally into it.

36
00:03:58,126 --> 00:03:59,425
Hey, Ran.

37
00:03:59,426 --> 00:04:02,125
When is that Wolf Face that was introduced a while ago going to fight?

38
00:04:02,126 --> 00:04:04,125
He's incredibly strong, isn't he?

39
00:04:04,126 --> 00:04:07,625
Wolf Face is fighting in the junior heavyweight title match,

40
00:04:07,626 --> 00:04:10,125
so it'll be at the very end, which is the main event!

41
00:04:10,126 --> 00:04:13,425
Are you saying that he's a champion or something like that?

42
00:04:13,426 --> 00:04:14,725
Right!

43
00:04:14,726 --> 00:04:16,225
After he debuted making an official announcement

44
00:04:16,226 --> 00:04:17,925
that he would take off his mask if he loses,

45
00:04:17,926 --> 00:04:21,326
but he never lost in all the single 65 matches he fought!

46
00:04:23,026 --> 00:04:26,625
But, I'd like to see him lose for once.

47
00:04:26,626 --> 00:04:28,625
Why?

48
00:04:28,626 --> 00:04:31,025
Because if he loses,

49
00:04:31,026 --> 00:04:32,925
