52
00:04:40,226 --> 00:04:43,026
Sorry for being an ugly man.

53
00:04:46,826 --> 00:04:50,125
But, he isn't bald.

54
00:04:50,126 --> 00:04:51,225
What?

55
00:04:51,226 --> 00:04:52,725
Then, don't tell me that...

56
00:04:52,726 --> 00:04:54,426
You're him?

57
00:04:57,426 --> 00:05:02,825
"Takaharu Ogami (27)" -This is the true identity of Wolf Face.

58
00:05:02,826 --> 00:05:04,225
Are you sure it's okay, though?

59
00:05:04,226 --> 00:05:06,625
Coming out without your mask to a place like this.

60
00:05:06,626 --> 00:05:07,725
No worry,

61
00:05:07,726 --> 00:05:11,425
Wolf Face is said to be Mexican.

62
00:05:11,426 --> 00:05:16,025
Besides, I sometimes fight in the opening performance with this face.

63
00:05:16,026 --> 00:05:19,525
But, everybody thinks that I'm just a young wrestler.

64
00:05:19,526 --> 00:05:22,825
Well, I don't use the techniques of Wolf Face at that time,

65
00:05:22,826 --> 00:05:25,025
