116
00:08:01,926 --> 00:08:03,525
Mr. Nagase.

117
00:08:03,526 --> 00:08:06,526
Mr. Nagase! Turn this way please.

118
00:08:09,926 --> 00:08:13,125
Mr. Nagase! You're finally going to be fighting against

119
00:08:13,126 --> 00:08:15,725
the invincible champion Wolf Face for his belt,

120
00:08:15,726 --> 00:08:17,725
