121
00:08:17,726 --> 00:08:20,025
How am I feeling?

122
00:08:20,026 --> 00:08:24,125
All I want is for the people here to watch me.

123
00:08:24,126 --> 00:08:27,025
To watch me fight with all my might

124
00:08:27,026 --> 00:08:29,025
"Hyota Nagase (25)" -against that idiot Japanese leopard

125
00:08:29,026 --> 00:08:33,725
