126
00:08:33,726 --> 00:08:35,525
Japanese leopard?

127
00:08:35,526 --> 00:08:39,225
You mean Wolf Face is Japanese?

128
00:08:39,226 --> 00:08:41,625
-Oh, no. -It's a joke, just a joke!

129
00:08:41,626 --> 00:08:44,926
We're in a rush, so interview us later.

130
00:08:46,126 --> 00:08:48,025
"Japanese Team Locker Room" -Hey, Nagase!

131
00:08:48,026 --> 00:08:49,725
Just what do you think you're doing?

132
00:08:49,726 --> 00:08:50,825
"Iwao Ushigome (36)" -Didn't I tell you

133
00:08:50,826 --> 00:08:53,725
