145
00:09:25,226 --> 00:09:26,825
Just what are you talking about?

146
00:09:26,826 --> 00:09:29,525
What's important for a wrestler is looks.

147
00:09:29,526 --> 00:09:31,625
If not, a wrestler with your ability

148
00:09:31,626 --> 00:09:34,725
