149
00:09:34,726 --> 00:09:36,126
What?

150
00:09:37,826 --> 00:09:39,425
Hey, Nagase!

151
00:09:39,426 --> 00:09:41,425
That's no way to talk to your superior.

152
00:09:41,426 --> 00:09:42,825
"Hiroyuki Sakuma (25)" -Hold it.

153
00:09:42,826 --> 00:09:47,425
You don't want to hurt a precious body just before a match, do you?

154
00:09:47,426 --> 00:09:48,725
Okay then.

155
00:09:48,726 --> 00:09:51,925
I'll be flexing my body like always in the room.

156
00:09:51,926 --> 00:09:54,026
So when it's time to fight the match, please call me.

157
00:09:55,326 --> 00:09:57,125
Well, if I win,

158
00:09:57,126 --> 00:10:00,425
I'll give all of you a mask as a gift.

159
00:10:00,426 --> 00:10:02,225
So that you guys can all hide your ugly faces

160
00:10:02,226 --> 00:10:04,926
