161
00:10:11,126 --> 00:10:13,825
Yeah. No problem.

162
00:10:13,826 --> 00:10:16,925
Chances are 200 percent my win.

163
00:10:16,926 --> 00:10:18,325
Although, it's a hidden fact,

164
00:10:18,326 --> 00:10:21,326
