167
00:10:29,726 --> 00:10:33,625
All I have to do is peel his mask off on the mat, that'll be it.

168
00:10:33,626 --> 00:10:35,825
Everything will work out just fine.

169
00:10:35,826 --> 00:10:38,825
I made the young ones at your place wear masks

170
00:10:38,826 --> 00:10:41,025
