00:11:39,126 --> 00:11:42,125
Amazing.

189
00:11:42,126 --> 00:11:44,426
He's so different from who we just saw.

190
00:11:45,526 --> 00:11:47,325
Hey, Wolf!

191
00:11:47,326 --> 00:11:50,026
"Leonardo Rossi (30)" -Good luck.

192
00:11:56,026 --> 00:11:59,525
Shoots. I better go to the restroom quickly.

