216
00:12:54,026 --> 00:12:55,325
Hey, Nagase!

217
00:12:55,326 --> 00:12:57,126
Hurry up and come out!

218
00:13:03,526 --> 00:13:05,625
Nagase?

219
00:13:05,626 --> 00:13:08,025
Hey, get a hold of yourself! Nagase!

220
00:13:08,026 --> 00:13:09,325
No good.

