244
00:14:43,134 --> 00:14:44,534
No way.

245
00:14:53,334 --> 00:14:57,933
The victim is Mr. Hyota Nagase, age 25.

246
00:14:57,934 --> 00:14:59,933
He belongs to the Teito Pro Wrestling team.

247
00:14:59,934 --> 00:15:01,733
A professional wrestler?

248
00:15:01,734 --> 00:15:05,333
